Package org.cesecore.keys.util

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ISignOperation
    An object of a class implementing this interface must be constructed before using SignWithWorkingAlgorithm.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    KeyPairWrapper
    Wrapper class for serializing KeyPair objects.
    KeyStoreTools  
    KeyTools
    Tools to handle common key and keystore operations.
    PublicKeyWrapper
    Wrapper class for serializing PublicKey objects.
    SignWithWorkingAlgorithm
    Call SignWithWorkingAlgorithm.doSignTask(List, Provider, ISignOperation) or SignWithWorkingAlgorithm.doSignTask(List, String, ISignOperation) when you want to sign with any working algorithm in the list.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    KeyUtilRuntimeException
    Exception thrown by classes in this package when an error occur that should not be handled.
    TaskWithSigningException
    Exception that may be thrown by the ISignOperation.taskWithSigning(String, java.security.Provider)
